---
import Ironside from "../../layouts/Ironside.astro";
import Placeholder from "../../components/PlaceholderImage.astro";
---

<Ironside title="Epoxy flooring Oakville" description="Oakville-owned polyaspartic garage floor specialists. 142 installs across 8 neighborhoods. Diamond-ground, 1-day install, lifetime warranty." heroType="dark">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero-dark">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grain"></div>
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="breadcrumb mono" style="color:var(--color-iron-300);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:24px">
      <a href="/service-areas" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:none;opacity:.7">Service areas</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span style="color:var(--accent)">Oakville</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kicker">Service area &middot; Oakville, Ontario</div>
    <h1 class="h-hero mt-3" style="max-width:20ch">Oakville&rsquo;s polyaspartic garage floor specialists.</h1>
    <p class="lede mt-4" style="max-width:58ch;color:var(--color-iron-300)">Oakville-owned, Oakville-operated. Our shop is on Wyecroft Road. Most jobs in Oakville are installed within 2&ndash;3 weeks of booking.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats mt-6">
      <div><div class="n mono">142</div><div class="l">Oakville installs</div></div>
      <div><div class="n mono">8</div><div class="l">Neighborhoods served</div></div>
      <div><div class="n mono">4.9</div><div class="l">Avg review (Oakville)</div></div>
      <div><div class="n mono">15</div><div class="l">Min avg drive to site</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY OAKVILLE CHOOSES IRONSIDE -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split-64" style="align-items:start">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Why Oakville chooses Ironside</div>
        <h2 class="h2 mt-2" style="max-width:20ch">We know your slab.</h2>
        <p class="lede mt-4">Oakville garages from the late-90s Bronte and Glen Abbey builds have high-chloride slabs that eat cheap epoxy alive. We moisture-test every floor before we quote it &mdash; and we won&rsquo;t pour polyaspartic over concrete that isn&rsquo;t ready.</p>
        <div style="display:grid;gap:20px;margin-top:32px">
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
            <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-iron-950);color:var(--accent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0">01</div>
            <div>
              <div class="h4">Local moisture testing</div>
              <div class="p" style="margin-top:4px;color:var(--fg2)">Calcium chloride test before every pour.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
            <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-iron-950);color:var(--accent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0">02</div>
            <div>
              <div class="h4">In-home consult, no pressure</div>
              <div class="p" style="margin-top:4px;color:var(--fg2)">Sample kit on your slab. Written quote in 48h.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:16px">
            <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-iron-950);color:var(--accent);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-mono-brand);font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0">03</div>
            <div>
              <div class="h4">Branded uniforms, photo updates</div>
              <div class="p" style="margin-top:4px;color:var(--fg2)">You know who&rsquo;s on your property.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Placeholder label="Oakville install &middot; Glen Abbey &middot; 04/26" aspect="4/5" variant="warm" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- NEIGHBORHOODS SERVED -->
<section class="section section-sm" style="background:var(--color-iron-50);border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-100);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-iron-100)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="kicker">Neighborhoods served</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8" style="max-width:18ch">Where we&rsquo;ve been this year.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px">
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">28 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Glen Abbey</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">24 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Bronte</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">21 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Lorne Park</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">19 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Oakville Trafalgar</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">17 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Uptown Core</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">14 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Old Oakville</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">11 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">Clearview</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:24px">
        <div class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em">8 INSTALLS</div>
        <div class="h4" style="margin-top:8px">West Oak Trails</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- RECENT OAKVILLE INSTALLS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="kicker">Recent Oakville installs</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8">Six jobs. Six neighborhoods.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px">
      <div><Placeholder label="Glen Abbey &middot; 04/26 &middot; Premium" aspect="4/3" variant="copper" /></div>
      <div><Placeholder label="Bronte &middot; 03/26 &middot; Standard" aspect="4/3" variant="dark" /></div>
      <div><Placeholder label="Lorne Park &middot; 03/26 &middot; Premium" aspect="4/3" variant="warm" /></div>
      <div><Placeholder label="Uptown Core &middot; 02/26 &middot; Essential" aspect="4/3" variant="concrete" /></div>
      <div><Placeholder label="Old Oakville &middot; 02/26 &middot; Premium" aspect="4/3" variant="copper" /></div>
      <div><Placeholder label="Clearview &middot; 01/26 &middot; Standard" aspect="4/3" variant="light" /></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- REVIEWS -->
<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="kicker">Reviews from Oakville</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8">What your neighbors say.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px">
      <div style="background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);padding:32px">
        <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.1em">&starf; &starf; &starf; &starf; &starf;</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:16px">Ironside diamond-ground our 22-year-old slab and laid polyaspartic in a single day. Truck was back in the garage 30 hours later. Warranty paperwork arrived by courier the next week.</p>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);margin-top:24px;padding-top:16px">
          <div style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">Mark D.</div>
          <div class="mono" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-iron-500);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">GLEN ABBEY &middot; PREMIUM &middot; 03/26</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);padding:32px">
        <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.1em">&starf; &starf; &starf; &starf; &starf;</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:16px">Got three quotes. Ironside was the most expensive and the only one who tested for moisture before quoting. That told me everything. Zero regrets.</p>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);margin-top:24px;padding-top:16px">
          <div style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">Priya S.</div>
          <div class="mono" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-iron-500);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">LORNE PARK &middot; PREMIUM &middot; 02/26</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-iron-900);border:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);padding:32px">
        <div class="mono" style="color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.1em">&starf; &starf; &starf; &starf; &starf;</div>
        <p style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:16px">Second Ironside floor &mdash; did my daughter&rsquo;s house in Bronte after ours held up for three years of hockey-bag abuse. That&rsquo;s my review.</p>
        <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-iron-800);margin-top:24px;padding-top:16px">
          <div style="color:var(--fg-inverse);font-weight:600">Tom H.</div>
          <div class="mono" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-iron-500);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-top:4px">BRONTE &middot; STANDARD &middot; 01/26</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="kicker">Oakville FAQ</div>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-2 mb-8">Questions specific to Oakville.</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details open>
        <summary><span>Do you pull Oakville building permits?</span><span class="chev">+</span></summary>
        <div class="a"><p>Residential garage coatings do not require a permit in the Town of Oakville. Basement coatings over 500 sqft may fall under a separate interior alteration permit &mdash; we&rsquo;ll walk you through it.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary><span>Can you coat my Glen Abbey slab? It&rsquo;s from 1998.</span><span class="chev">+</span></summary>
        <div class="a"><p>Most likely yes &mdash; but we&rsquo;ll do a calcium chloride moisture test and surface profile check before we quote. Older Glen Abbey pours often have high-chloride content; polyaspartic is actually the better choice there.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary><span>What&rsquo;s your Oakville lead time?</span><span class="chev">+</span></summary>
        <div class="a"><p>2&ndash;3 weeks typical between signed quote and install day. Peak season (May&ndash;Aug) may stretch to 4 weeks.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary><span>Do you do condos or townhomes?</span><span class="chev">+</span></summary>
        <div class="a"><p>Yes &mdash; private garages only. We do not bid on shared underground condo lots or property-managed buildings.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BAND -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="kicker">Oakville booking</div>
        <h2 class="h1 mt-2" style="color:var(--fg-inverse);max-width:22ch">We can probably be at your place next week.</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;align-items:flex-end">
        <a href="/quote" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" style="min-width:260px">Get my free quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9055550174" class="btn btn-lg btn-ghost-dark" style="min-width:260px">905 &middot; 555 &middot; 0174</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Ironside>

